snippet.title: D Abdul - SONE KI CHIDYA ft. Adnaan 07 | Official Music Video | Prod by - Waynem
snippet.description:
This song is all about the current situation of India. The track “Sone Ki Chidya” includes issues which people are facing due to COVID-19, dirty politics, paid news and much more related to our country. The main motive of “Sone Ki Chidya” is to aware people from all these things.
